data.description: Welcome home to this wonderful 4-bed, 2-bath home located in the gated community of Hammock Creek. This super private home is nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac and backs up to a lush preserve; you don’t want to miss this lot! The split plan is centered entirely on the kitchen, which is the true heart of this home. There’s plenty of cabinet and counter space, as well as an eating bar that overlooks the family room. Expansive ceilings maximize the use of natural light throughout. Don’t miss the view to the patio, complete with an electric retractable awning, so you can spend just as much time outdoors enjoying the view. This house is perfect for entertaining, with a formal dining room adjacent to the entry way sitting area. Plenty of space for all your guests! The master suite is equipped with two walk-in closets and dual vanities and a magnificent view of the back yard through expansive sliding glass doors. Enjoy quick access to I-95 and the turnpike, as well as all Palm City has to offer
